### Variables locales
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@token = pega_aqui_un_token_jwt

### Test inicial
GET http://localhost:3001/

### Registro exitoso
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "passwordConfirm": "Password123"
}

### Login exitoso
POST @baseUrl/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Crear perfil social autenticado
POST @baseUrl/profiles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Cano Joel",
  "url": "https://instagram.com/canojoel",
  "platform": "INSTAGRAM"
}

### Alias sin /api para probar el endpoint solicitado
POST http://localhost:3001/profiles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Cano Joel",
  "url": "https://tiktok.com/@canojoel",
  "platform": "TIKTOK"
}
